---
title: Italian Ciabatta Burgers with Caramelized Onion, Mozzarella, and Sweet-and-Tangy Arugula Salad
description: For an Italian spin on the classic American cheeseburger, we’re sandwiching juicy patties between crusty ciabatta bread, then topping them with gooey cheeses and sweet caramelized onions. A garlicky, tomato-balsamic vinaigrette sets this arugula salad apart from the standard side dish.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/56411f694dab7112428b4567.jpg
